                        <interp inst="t18540814-name-384" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN BONE</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, H</hi> 122). I produce the two certificates of mar<lb></lb>riage; I have compared them with the book, they are correct.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined. Q.</hi> Where did you take the prisoner? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> On Friars' Mount, on 10th July—he said he thought he was at liberty to many, not having lived with his wife for seven years—I know the prisoner, he had a good character. (<hi rend="italic">The prisoner received a good character.</hi>)</p>
